qMeasure.qLabel: TG - Uptake at least one dose (%)
qMeasure.qDef:
pick(match(v_ViewTargetGroup , '80', 'HCW', 'LTCF'),
 	dual(if([Vaccination.YearWeek]=MaxString(total [Vaccination.YearWeek]),
    	num(median({<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr( sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_80_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_80_Cumul), [Member State], [Vaccination.YearWeek])), '0.0%') , ''),
    		median({<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr( sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_80_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_80_Cumul), [Member State], [Vaccination.YearWeek]))),  
    
    dual(if([Vaccination.YearWeek]=MaxString(total [Vaccination.YearWeek]),  
    	num(median({<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr( sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul), [Member State], [Vaccination.YearWeek])), '0.0%'), ''),
    		median({<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr( sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul), [Member State], [Vaccination.YearWeek]))), 
    
    dual(if([Vaccination.YearWeek]=MaxString(total [Vaccination.YearWeek]),  
    	num(median({<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr( sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul), [Member State], [Vaccination.YearWeek])), '0.0%'), ''),
    		median({<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr( sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul), [Member State], [Vaccination.YearWeek])))
)
